145
00:13:17,620 --> 00:13:20,220
[SPEAKER_00] Kako će oni ovladati Hethlando?

146
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:27,960
[SPEAKER_00] A Hethland je ovoće njegov misao, bio geostrateg, engleski Sir Hartford Mackinder.

147
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:32,100
